- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/websockets/ws/commit/4abd8f6de4b0b65ef80b3ff081989479ed93377e)
- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/websockets/ws/commit/e55e5106f10fcbaac37cfa89759e4cc0d073a52c)
- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/websockets/ws/commit/eeb76d313e2a00dd5247ca3597bba7877d064a63)
- [GitHub Issue](https://github.com/websockets/ws/issues/2230)
